original_title: Mastering Leadership Series Vol. 3: Your New Dog First Day and Beyond
overview: Start off on the right paw with Volume 3 of Cesar’s best-selling DVD series, Cesar’s hands-on guide to selecting the perfect dog for your family, selecting a dog that matches your energy, bringing a puppy home for the first time and more.
title: Mastering Leadership Series Vol. 3: Your New Dog First Day and Beyond
